items.name: HabitSphere
items.description: HabitSphere  is a dynamic habit-tracking application designed to help you build and maintain positive habits effortlessly. With an intuitive interface and features like a daily habit checklist, progress tracking, and a heatmap visualization, HabitSphere empowers users to stay consistent and achieve their goals.
